#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Kimi-K2.5.md:131
msgid "5.1 Single-Node Online Deployment"
msgstr "5.1 单节点在线部署"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Kimi-K2.5.md:133
msgid ""
"Single-node deployment completes both Prefill and Decode within the same "
"node. The quantized model `Kimi-K2.5-w4a8` can be deployed on 1 Atlas 800"
" A3 (64G × 16)."
msgstr "单节点部署在同一节点内完成 Prefill 和 Decode。量化模型 `Kimi-K2.5-w4a8` 可以部署在 1 台 Atlas 800 A3（64G × 16）上。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Kimi-K2.5.md:135
msgid "Run the following script to execute online inference."
msgstr "运行以下脚本执行在线推理。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Kimi-K2.5.md:137
#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Kimi-K2.5.md:249
